            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>S</abbr><ex>oli</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>nvicto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>eo</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Livanius</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan> <lb n="3"/>Senecio <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>vet</abbr><ex>eranus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>egionis</ex></expan> XIIII <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>g</abbr><ex>eminae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Mittelteil und crepido eines Altars oder einer Basis. Z. 2: überliefert ist IIVI[-]IVS und LIVAIVS oder LIVANVS (mit AI- oder ANIV-Ligatur); Kubitschek; AE 1907: Livinius(?); Kremer: Livinius. (B): CIMRM: Z. 4/5: Zeilenfall nicht angegeben; Kubitschek Z. 5: s(olvi)t; Hild: Z. 2: Liv[ini?]us.</p>
            </div>
